ause it generates data embedded in a very high dimensional space\nwithout driving fluid mechanical instabilities, and is agnostic to the flow\nprotocol.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Oct 2019 03:52:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Feb 2022 17:12:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 10 Feb 2022 17:38:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-11"}
