iple technical features using various frameworks: random surfer\nmodels, similarity-based grouping, MMR-like re-ranking, or combinatorial\noptimization. We also found a few deep learning based methods in recent\nresearch.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Oct 2019 04:02:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 May 2021 02:22:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-12"}
