e. If the metamodel is correct, it will be able\nto compute as Telemac would do but with a highly reduced computational cost.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Oct 2019 15:19:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-24"}
